msgid "Set SVG sincronizzato da <code>npm</code> (<code>sh tools/sync_ionicons.sh</code>): manifest statico <code>ionicons-manifest.json</code> e ricerca client-side nella galleria."
msgstr "SVG set synced from <code>npm</code> (<code>sh tools/sync_ionicons.sh</code>): static <code>ionicons-manifest.json</code> manifest and client-side search in the gallery."

msgid "Tema scuro e marchio"
msgstr "Dark theme & brand"

msgid "Attributo <code>data-velora-theme=\"dark\"</code> su <code>&lt;html&gt;</code>, preferenze in <code>localStorage</code> (chiave <code>velora-theme</code>). Più il tag standalone <code>velora_logo</code> e la barra segmenti <code>velora_satisfaction_bar</code>."
msgstr "<code>data-velora-theme=\"dark\"</code> on <code>&lt;html&gt;</code>, preference in <code>localStorage</code> (key <code>velora-theme</code>). Plus the standalone <code>velora_logo</code> tag and the <code>velora_satisfaction_bar</code> segments."

